#: chapter-charts.xml:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "AREASPLINE"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: classname
#: chapter-charts.xml:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "PlotOptionsAreaSpline"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: parameter
#: chapter-charts.xml:420
#, no-c-format
msgid "AREARANGE"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: classname
#: chapter-charts.xml:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "PlotOptionsAreaRange"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: parameter
#: chapter-charts.xml:424
#, no-c-format
msgid "AREASPLINERANGE"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: classname
#: chapter-charts.xml:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "PlotOptionsAreaSplineRange"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-charts.xml:431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In area range charts, the area between a lower and upper value is painted "
"with a transparent color. The data series must specify the minimum and "
"maximum values for the Y coordinates, defined either with "
"<classname>RangeSeries</classname>, as described in <xref linkend=\"charts."
"data.rangeseries\"/>, or with <classname>DataSeries</classname>, described "
"in <xref linkend=\"charts.data.dataseries\"/>."
msgstr ""
"在面积范围图(Area Range Chart)中, 位于数值下限与上限之间的面积会使用透明颜色"
"描绘. 数据序列必须指定为 Y 坐标之星最小和最大值, 最小和最大值可以使用 "
"<classname>RangeSeries</classname> 来定义, 详情请参见 <xref linkend=\"charts."
"data.rangeseries\"/>, 也可以使用 <classname>DataSeries</classname> 来定义, 详"
"情请参见 <xref linkend=\"charts.data.dataseries\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-charts.xml:444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Area charts support <emphasis>stacking</emphasis>, so that multiple series "
"are piled on top of each other. You enable stacking from the plot options "
"with <methodname>setStacking()</methodname>. The <parameter>Stacking.NORMAL</"
"parameter> stacking mode does a normal summative stacking, while the "
"<parameter>Stacking.PERCENT</parameter> handles them as proportions."
msgstr ""
"面积图支持 <emphasis>堆栈</emphasis> 模式, 因此多个数据序列会层叠式的堆积在一"
"起. 你可以使用绘图选项的 <methodname>setStacking()</methodname> 方法来启用堆"
"栈模式. <parameter>Stacking.NORMAL</parameter> 模式使用通常的合计叠加方式, "
"<parameter>Stacking.PERCENT</parameter> 模式则使用相对比例来显示数据."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-charts.xml:453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The fill color for the area is defined with the <parameter>fillColor</"
"parameter> property and its transparency with <parameter>fillOpacity</"
"parameter> (the opposite of transparency) with a value between 0.0 and 1.0."
msgstr ""
"面积的填充色由 <parameter>fillColor</parameter> 属性控制, 透明度由 "
"<parameter>fillOpacity</parameter> 属性控制 (这个属性设置的是\"不透明度\"), "
"这个属性的有效值在 0.0 到 1.0 之间."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-charts.xml:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Column and Bar Charts"
msgstr "柱形图(Column Chart)与条形图(Bar Chart)"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-charts.xml:478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Column and bar charts illustrate values as vertical or horizontal bars, "
"respectively. The two chart types are essentially equivalent, just as if the "
"orientation of the axes was inverted."
msgstr ""
"柱形图与条形图分别使用垂直和水平的棒图来显示数据. 这两种图表本质上是一样的, "
"只是数据轴的方向不同."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-charts.xml:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Multiple data series, that is, two-dimensional data, are shown with thinner "
"bars or columns grouped by their category, as described in <xref linkend="
"\"charts.basic-use.two-dimensional\"/>. Enabling stacking with "
"<methodname>setStacking()</methodname> in plot options stacks the columns or "
"bars of different series on top of each other."
msgstr ""
"多个数据序列, 也就是, 二维数据, 会通过各自的种别进行分组, 然后显示为较细的横"
"条或竖柱, 详情请参见 <xref linkend=\"charts.basic-use.two-dimensional\"/>. 可"
"以使用绘图选项的 <methodname>setStacking()</methodname> 方法来启用堆栈模式, "
"堆栈模式将把不同数据序列的横条或竖柱叠加起来显示."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-charts.xml:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also have <parameter>COLUMNRANGE</parameter> charts that illustrate "
"a range between a lower and an upper value, as described in <xref linkend="
"\"charts.charttypes.rangecharts\"/>. They require the use of "
"<classname>RangeSeries</classname> for defining the lower and upper values."
msgstr ""
"你也可以使用 <parameter>COLUMNRANGE</parameter> 图表, 它显示数值下限与上限之"
"间的一个范围, 详情请参见 <xref linkend=\"charts.charttypes.rangecharts\"/>. "
"范围图表需要使用 <classname>RangeSeries</classname> 来定义数值的下限和上限."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-charts.xml:501
#, no-c-format
msgid "Column and Bar Chart Subtypes"
msgstr "柱形图与条形图的子类型"

